subproject.corporate outcome: Strengthened capacities of national human rights institutions
subproject.description: The project focuses on developing a legislative electoral framework in line with international standards; enhancing Central Elections Committee and Regional Elections Committees capacity to plan, prepare and conduct polling and implement best electoral management practices. It also increases opportunities for candidates, mass media representatives and domestic observers to participate effectively in the political process.
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: Electoral System and Processes

title: Enhancing Electoral System and Processes in Turkmenistan
